      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEMENTIA (1) took the sit on the lead but levelled up to score (17.62) at this track in a Maiden over 300m. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. One of the key runners again. BANJO'S FERNANDO (2) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (17.87) at this track. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Expected to feature again. RIVERSIDE LEVI (8) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 5th (20.41) at Grafton. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Should be in this for a long way. MERCURIAL HIGH (5) must be included in calculations.",
